{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"毛主席穿军装","authors":["高红纯"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席穿军装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门城楼上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光万道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日当空照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山呼海啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人海如潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万面红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百万雄师把拳头举得高高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐声欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席穿着军装来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军含着幸福的泪在笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵含着幸福的泪在笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红卫兵”含着幸福的泪在笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民都是兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都含着抑制不住的幸福的泪在笑……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的统帅，英明的领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十多年前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您穿上军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把红军缔造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您点燃的中国武装斗争的烈火遍地燃烧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的统帅，英明的领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗日战争时期，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您穿上军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导抗日的军民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭了日本法西斯强盗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的统帅，英明的领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第三次国内革命战争时期，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您穿上军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导全国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打垮了蒋家王朝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，我们最敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您又穿上军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导我们保卫祖国的江山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果敌人胆敢来侵犯，就把它彻底埋葬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门城楼上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光万道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日当空照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山呼海啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人海如潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万面红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民把拳头举得高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐声欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最热烈地欢呼啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的毛主席穿着军装来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军某部　高红纯"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"武汉地区无产阶级革命派百万雄师联络站（百万雄师）","type":"人物"},{"name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}